title: Eagles parade had 'more people than the Trump inauguration': Philly mayor
text:
Eagles parade had 'more people than the Trump inauguration': Philly mayor 3:44pm EST - 00:54 
Philadelphia mayor Jim Kenney joked on Friday that the Eagles parade, which was estimated to have attracted about two million fans, had 'more people than the Trump inauguration'.
